    {
      "num": 1,
      "geez": "ዘተጽሕፈ፡ እምሄኖክ፡ ጸሐፈ፡ ዝ፡ ኵሉ፡ ትምህርተ፡ ጥበብ፡ እምኵሉ፡ ሰብእ፡ ስቡሕ፡ ወመኰንነ፡ ኵሉ፡ ምድር፡ ለኵሎሙ፡ ውሉድየ፡ እለ፡ የኀድሩ፡ ዲበ፡ ምድር፡ ወለትውልድ፡ ደኃራውያን፡ እለ፡ ይገብሩ፡ ርትዐ፡ ወሰላመ።",
      "translation": "The book written by Enoch—[Enoch indeed wrote this complete doctrine of wisdom, (which is) praised of all men and a judge of all the earth] for all my children who shall dwell on the earth. And for the future generations who shall observe uprightness and peace.",
